{"id": "3970", "title": "Bug 3970[preferences] UI needed to define the default line delimiters for new files (1GFIOAX)", "description": "Bug 3970[preferences] UI needed to define the default line delimiters for new files (1GFIOAX). The Windows workstations are used as X terminals and to run Eclipse (since PCs are cheaper than Unix boxes).", "OB": "When creating a new file, the line delimiter used is currently determined by the value returned from System.getProperties("line.delimiter"). However, this may not always be what the user wants.", "EB": "", "SR": "To reproduce the issue, follow these steps: 

